fields.name: Fit Six Branded Zip Hoodie
fields.description:
Built for comfort and recovery, this full-zip Fit Six hoodie is a staple for both gym sessions and rest days.
Crafted from soft, pre-shrunk fleece with a brushed interior, it delivers warmth, comfort, and durability—perfect for layering on your way to training or winding down post-workout.

fields.name: Fit Six Branded Hoodie
fields.description:
This classic Fit Six hoodie blends comfort and simplicity for everyday training.
Built with a soft cotton-faced fabric and a relaxed fit, it’s ideal for warming up, cooling down, or repping the brand on rest days.

fields.name: Fit Six Branded T-Shirt
fields.description: Stay dry and move freely in the Fit Six performance tee. Built with moisture-wicking fabric to keep you cool during tough sessions, its athletic cut offers a clean, flattering fit for every body type.

fields.name: Fit Six Branded Sweatshirt
fields.description: The Fit Six heavyweight crew is built for comfort and recovery. Ideal for warm-ups, cool-downs, or rest days, this cosy classic delivers a snug fit that feels just right—whether you’re heading to the gym or kicking back in style.

fields.name: Fit Six Branded Vest
fields.description: This lightweight gym vest is built for performance and comfort. Featuring moisture-wicking fabric to keep you cool and dry, its athletic fit allows full range of motion while offering a flattering silhouette for all body types.
